window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Life is quiet for Alex Verus. Amazing. With a flat full of friends (and the occasional fish) and business booming, why not enjoy the humdrum here and now? </p> <p>But of course that's too good to be true. In a sudden and cruel pincer movement of fate, Alex finds himself fighting a sinister and powerful gang as well as his own demons - for the same crime. </p> <p>Held hostage by the choices of his past, Alex's future is now in jeopardy.... </p>"; 
